channel.title: Mood - Octavo [Trey remix, given new life in FB]
channel.description:
Hey guys I just uploaded my next track! Its pretty good, and its my first upload of a future bass track! I don't know if you repost remixes or not @Auxy but I think youll want to consider this one. :smile: Thanks to @Ninjendo for letting me remix! There's some tasty chords in there for @MR_ANDERSON and some wubs for @Produk and @aUstin_Haga. Hope you guys like it. As always, open to any feedback! [https://soundcloud.com/trey-218274248/mood-octavo-trey-remix](https://soundcloud.com/trey-218274248/mood-octavo-trey-remix)
Also, here is the original track: [https://soundcloud.com/octavomusic/mood](https://soundcloud.com/octavomusic/mood)
